Iblis Berkuda Besi Yan Guigui
juga tiba-tiba muncul,

00:34:54.670 --> 00:34:56.449
[Elder, Raja Ular Geng Kuasa]
[Chi Li, Gadis Raja Ular]

00:34:55.710 --> 00:34:56.960
mengganggu rancangan saya.

